<subSubSection pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,944,1187]" box="[151,572,944,971]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,530,944,971]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Number of specimens recorded.</emphasis>
45.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,944,1187]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,980,1007]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Distribution.</emphasis>
Thus far only known from 
<collectingCountry box="[664,748,981,1007]" name="Algeria" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Algeria</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Vaillant, F." box="[763,920,980,1007]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="35 - 40" refId="ref35921" refString="Vaillant, F. (1952) Contribution a l'etude des Dolichopodidae d'Algerie (Dipteres) I. Bulletin de la Societe d'histoire naturelle d'Afrique du Nord, 41 (5 - 6), 35 - 40." type="journal article" year="1952">Vaillant 1952</bibRefCitation>
), first record for Europe! 
<collectingCountry box="[1211,1310,981,1007]" name="Portugal" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: four provinces, all over the country.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,944,1187]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1053,1079]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Ecology.</emphasis>
This species has been retrieved from a variety of habitat 
<typeStatus box="[943,1002,1053,1079]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">types</typeStatus>
featuring canopy by shrubs or trees. It was collected in highest numbers (14 and 
<specimenCount box="[622,775,1089,1116]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" type="generic">18 specimens</specimenCount>
) at two locations in Ribatejo.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,944,1187]" box="[199,524,1124,1151]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,1124,1151]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
5.7 (fairly rare).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,944,1187]" box="[199,701,1160,1187]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,1160,1187]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Activity period.</emphasis>
March–May, July–October.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
